# DysButton@Button â€” Composant rÃ©utilisable
# Usage dans .kv : DysButton: (hÃ©rite de Button avec le style DYS)
# Usage en Python : Factory.DysButton(text="...", on_press=...)
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
<DysButton@Button>:
    font_name: "OpenDyslexic"
    font_size: "24sp"
    size_hint_y: None
    height: "56dp"                              # > 48dp minimum (Â§3 skill)
    background_color: 0.26, 0.52, 0.96, 1      # bleu doux
    color: 1, 1, 1, 1
    background_normal: ""
    background_down: ""
    border: [0, 0, 0, 0]
    canvas.before:
        Color:
            rgba: (0.20, 0.44, 0.86, 1) if self.state == 'down' else (0.26, 0.52, 0.96, 1)
        RoundedRectangle:
            pos: self.pos
            size: self.size
            radius: [dp(12), dp(12), dp(12), dp(12)]


