# DysTextInput@TextInput â€” Composant rÃ©utilisable
# Usage dans .kv : DysTextInput: (hÃ©rite de TextInput avec le style DYS)
# âš ï¸  RÃˆGLE  : Dans un [] Ã©valuÃ© par le Builder KV, utiliser dp(n) (appel de
#             fonction), JAMAIS "12dp" (chaÃ®ne) ni 12dp (littÃ©ral invalide).
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
<DysTextInput@TextInput>:
    font_name: "OpenDyslexic"
    font_size: "24sp"
    foreground_color: 0.15, 0.15, 0.20, 1
    background_color: 1, 1, 1, 0               # transparent â€” fond gÃ©rÃ© par canvas
    cursor_color: 0.26, 0.52, 0.96, 1
    size_hint_y: None
    height: "56dp"
    padding: [dp(16), dp(14), dp(16), dp(14)]   # [left, top, right, bottom]
    multiline: False
    hint_text_color: 0.60, 0.60, 0.65, 1
    canvas.before:
        Color:
            rgba: 0.93, 0.91, 0.85, 1          # crÃ¨me lÃ©gÃ¨rement plus foncÃ© que le fond
        RoundedRectangle:
            pos: self.pos
            size: self.size
            radius: [dp(10), dp(10), dp(10), dp(10)]
        Color:
            rgba: (0.26, 0.52, 0.96, 1) if self.focus else (0.75, 0.73, 0.68, 1)
        Line:
            rounded_rectangle: [self.x, self.y, self.width, self.height, dp(10)]
            width: 2


